item.title: Nvidia Stock Analysis
item.description: I’ve been interested in investing in the stock market lately. I thought doing this project might help me learn more about valuing companies and deciding what stocks to invest in. This is a short project where I analyse Nvidia stocks using past information. Some key questions that I wanted to answer in this project are: What was the change in price of stock over time? What was the daily, monthly, and yearly return of the stock?
